data.title: Marketing Analysis: Britannia
data.meta_description: Marketing Analysis: Britannia - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an overview and background of Britannia Industries Limited, a leading Indian biscuit manufacturer. It discusses the company's origins in Kolkata in 1892 and its growth into one of India's largest food brands. The document also summarizes several of Britannia's popular biscuit products including Nutri Choice 5 Gain, Tiger Banana, NutriChoice Sugerout, Britannia 50-50, and Nutri Choice Digestive Biscuits. It outlines Britannia's marketing strategies and market segmentation approaches.
